text: Maryana Ivanishyn (born 24 August 1992) is a Ukrainian footballer who plays as a defender and has appeared for the Ukraine women's national team. ==Career== Ivanishyn has been capped for the Ukraine national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian women's footballers Category:Ukraine women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders Category:AC Sparta Praha (women) players Category:Expatriate women's footballers in the Czech Republic Category:Ukrainian expatriate sportspeople in the Czech Republic Category:Czech First Division (women) players
title: Maryana Ivanishyn
